scene.message:
Nanjo: {ctl0f:1}...{wait_fr:48}{nl}
Sorry, but my mind isn't{wait_fr:32}{nl}
as sharp as usual.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I want to help Maki's{nl}
mother soon...{wait_fr:32}{nl}
Come with me to Alaya Shrine!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: The air in this town{nl}
feels like it's changed.{nl}
It's somehow hard to breathe.{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: There's a kind of haze{nl}
hanging outside the window.{nl}
It seems to surround the town.{waitkey}Surely we can't be trapped in{nl}
this town like in some weird{nl}
novel... There's no way that{nl}
could happen, right?{waitkey}{ret}

Old Man: Hiroshi, it's been a{nl}
while. Have you come to hear{nl}
me talk? Then I'll tell you{nl}
something worthwhile.{waitkey}Stay calm, think well, and{nl}
then act. Do that, and you'll{nl}
surely reach it...{wait_fr:48} the truth.{waitkey}By the way, Akiko, is lunch{nl}
not ready yet?{waitkey}{ret}
